      <a href="https://px.a8.net/svt/ejp?a8mat=4AXI0D+EEKKOI+3XCC+BXQOI" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" class="track-affiliate" data-broker="matsui_ideco_sticky" style="background-color: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 0.6rem 1rem; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem;">
        松井証券で詳しく見る
